snippet.title: Football Manager 2021 | Release Date | #FM21 Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Football Manager 2021 debuts November 24 on PC/Mac.

Pre-purchase any time before launch to get Early Access and secure 10% off. Participating digital retailers only 👉 http://fm21.store/Pre-purchase

Football Manager will also return to Xbox for the first time since the 2007/08 season. Release date TBC. Modelled on our popular Touch series, the Football Manager 2021 Xbox Edition will be a Play Anywhere title meaning it can be enjoyed on Xbox One, Series X and S, and any Windows 10 PC. 

Football Manager Touch and Mobile also return for the new season across iOS, Android and Switch. 

For the latest feature news, platform details and release information please visit http://fm21.store/Pre-purchase
